videos.description: Aaren Vaughns takes the pitch and sprints 71-yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Utah State's Vaughns takes reverse to the house

videos.description: Gerold Bright finds daylight and streaks in to the end zone for the long score.
videos.headline: Utah State's Bright rips off 75-yard TD

videos.description: Timothy McVey takes the toss and runs in untouched for the score.
videos.headline: McVey runs it in for Air Force TD

videos.description: Ja'Marcus Ingram jumps up to snag the interception to give the ball back to the Aggies.
videos.headline: Utah State picks off Sanders

videos.headline: Hunt runs it for Utah State TD

videos.headline: Air Force takes the lead with TD

videos.headline: Air Force gets stuffed from 1-yard line

videos.description: Jordan Love completes to Ron'quavion Tarver on a back shoulder fade for the score.
videos.headline: Love lobs up to Tarver for Utah State TD

videos.description: Grant Ross gets the strip sack and Santo Coppola recovers for the Air Force touchdown.
videos.headline: Strip sack leads to Falcons TD

videos.description: Jordan Love and Ron'quavion Tarver run the back-shoulder to perfection again as the Aggies take the lead.
videos.headline: Love hits Tarver again for Utah State TD
